lynx(1) doesn't read from the freedesktop applications data (typeically at
/usr/share/applications/), so we bring the freedesktop applications data to
lynx(1).

== Documentation ==
See the POD embedded in the script; can be read with
	perldoc -F xdg2lynxcfg.pl

== Copyight ==
Again, see the POD (section `COPYRIGHT'); there is also SPDX metadata in
comments at the top of the script
